{"tid":201150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夢想換POSTCARD","createTime":"2017-04-14T14:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T14:12:53.000Z","uid":13330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8bdeb679a3e65d0206456878f40591d09dd7a0","tid":201150,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我之前印咗D postcard 諗住玩postcrossing 同用黎派<br />\n張咭係我自己畫自己design<br />\n係講一隻彈跳力好勁嘅雀仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/14/220556_3d0d52e5e57805d1fbb61ad9a5cd7ce7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2F220556_3d0d52e5e57805d1fbb61ad9a5cd7ce7.jpg&h=30e6af68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想以呢張咭去鼓勵同感染其他人<br />\n唔好放棄夢想<br />\n有興趣嘅朋友請幫我填咗以下張form<br />\n以你嘅夢想同我交換吖<br />\n(名額50，先到先得)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1GWqW-JCGMRbbo6A9MkeOa_QIHrK3lE-RnQ_TybNhsJo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1GWqW-JCGMRbbo6A9MkeOa_QIHrK3lE-RnQ_TybNhsJo%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f6204e7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1GWqW-JCGMRbbo6A9MkeOa_QIHrK3lE-RnQ_TybNhsJo/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/14/220727_0e369c3a56dcfd0ab42e3a6985d19389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2F220727_0e369c3a56dcfd0ab42e3a6985d19389.jpg&h=b113038e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b7e5f5b6b75a98c4d42801d0899378651bdea8","tid":201150,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc087b3e35290360887c223d16081abe1cec74b8","tid":201150,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"